29#ifndef ISCCC_CC_H
30#define ISCCC_CC_H 1
31
32/*! \file isccc/cc.h */
33
34#include <inttypes.h>
35#include <stdbool.h>
36
37#include <isc/lang.h>
38#include <isc/buffer.h>
39#include <isccc/types.h>
40
41ISC_LANG_BEGINDECLS
42
43/*% from lib/dns/include/dst/dst.h */
44
45#define ISCCC_ALG_UNKNOWN 0
46#define ISCCC_ALG_HMACMD5 157
47#define ISCCC_ALG_HMACSHA1 161
48#define ISCCC_ALG_HMACSHA224 162
49#define ISCCC_ALG_HMACSHA256 163
50#define ISCCC_ALG_HMACSHA384 164
51#define ISCCC_ALG_HMACSHA512 165
52
53/*% Maximum Datagram Package */
54#define ISCCC_CC_MAXDGRAMPACKET 4096
55
56/*% Message Type String */
57#define ISCCC_CCMSGTYPE_STRING 0x00
58/*% Message Type Binary Data */
59#define ISCCC_CCMSGTYPE_BINARYDATA 0x01
60/*% Message Type Table */
61#define ISCCC_CCMSGTYPE_TABLE 0x02
62/*% Message Type List */
63#define ISCCC_CCMSGTYPE_LIST 0x03
64
65/*% Send to Wire */
66isc_result_t
67isccc_cc_towire(isccc_sexpr_t *alist, isc_buffer_t **buffer,
68 uint32_t algorithm, isccc_region_t *secret);
69
70/*% Get From Wire */
71isc_result_t
72isccc_cc_fromwire(isccc_region_t *source, isccc_sexpr_t **alistp,
73 uint32_t algorithm, isccc_region_t *secret);
74
75/*% Create Message */
76isc_result_t
77isccc_cc_createmessage(uint32_t version, const char *from, const char *to,
78 uint32_t serial, isccc_time_t now,
79 isccc_time_t expires, isccc_sexpr_t **alistp);
80
81/*% Create Acknowledgment */
82isc_result_t
83isccc_cc_createack(isccc_sexpr_t *message, bool ok,
84 isccc_sexpr_t **ackp);
85
86/*% Is Ack? */
87bool
88isccc_cc_isack(isccc_sexpr_t *message);
89
90/*% Is Reply? */
91bool
92isccc_cc_isreply(isccc_sexpr_t *message);
93
94/*% Create Response */
95isc_result_t
96isccc_cc_createresponse(isccc_sexpr_t *message, isccc_time_t now,
97 isccc_time_t expires, isccc_sexpr_t **alistp);
98
99/*% Define String */
100isccc_sexpr_t *
101isccc_cc_definestring(isccc_sexpr_t *alist, const char *key, const char *str);
102
103/*% Define uint 32 */
104isccc_sexpr_t *
105isccc_cc_defineuint32(isccc_sexpr_t *alist, const char *key, uint32_t i);
106
107/*% Lookup String */
108isc_result_t
109isccc_cc_lookupstring(isccc_sexpr_t *alist, const char *key, char **strp);
110
111/*% Lookup uint 32 */
112isc_result_t
113isccc_cc_lookupuint32(isccc_sexpr_t *alist, const char *key,
114 uint32_t *uintp);
115
116/*% Create Symbol Table */
117isc_result_t
118isccc_cc_createsymtab(isccc_symtab_t **symtabp);
119
120/*% Clean up Symbol Table */
121void
122isccc_cc_cleansymtab(isccc_symtab_t *symtab, isccc_time_t now);
123
124/*% Check for Duplicates */
125isc_result_t
126isccc_cc_checkdup(isccc_symtab_t *symtab, isccc_sexpr_t *message,
127 isccc_time_t now);
128
129ISC_LANG_ENDDECLS
130
131#endif /* ISCCC_CC_H */
